{
  "texts": [
    "Chen et al.",
    "(5) developed a knowledge graph using 120 ancient stroke case records as a data source, achieving \"graph-number mutual verification\" through semantic data analysis and visualization of the graph.",
    "Wang et al.",
    "(6) developed a knowledge graph that encapsulates the clinical practices of esteemed TCM practitioners in managing coronary heart disease.",
    "This graph facilitates visualization and querying of their diagnostic and therapeutic methods."
  ]
}